$ Registry: HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\BCD00000000

This key stores the *boot configuration data* that is needed to → Windows/booting[boot up] the → Windows system.

In an → hardware/UEFI[UEFI] boot, the hive is stored in `/EFI/Microsoft/Boot/BCD`.
-
In a → hardware/BIOS[BIOS] boot, the hive is located in `/boot/BCD`.

The data should be edited with `bcdedit.exe`, not with → Windows/registry/regedit[regedit.exe].
